VariableDescription
surveydateDate of survey
psuPrimary sampling unit identifier
sexSex of child

heightheight of child in centimetres
oedemaDoes the child have oedema? 0 = FALSE; 1 = TRUE
muacMid-upper arm circumference in millimetres
